&lt;p&gt;Experience &amp;amp; Requirements&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You bring 10+ years of experience within the FCA-regulated payments, e-money, crypto, or banking sectors. You’ve spent at least 3-5 of those years in a senior leadership or Head of Compliance capacity, navigating the complexities of the UK regulatory landscape.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You have a proven ability to act as a force multiplier for executive leadership, managing cross-functional strategic initiatives and motivating teams to deliver under pressure.&lt;/li&gt;
